metadata.name: Ophelia
metadata.description:
This piece is about my self visual perception of Ophelia of Millais but with my own story. My story is about a bride who thought that  found her soulmate but she lost own. it Is about a person who think marriage is the begging of the happiness but if you don’t love yourself and don’t find yourself you can’t find another one.

Digital paint
1540 * 2000 PX
